snippet.title: Algebraic Expressions, Terms, and Coefficients
snippet.description:
Get the full course at: http://www.MathTutorDVD.com
In this lesson, you'll learn how to identify the parts of an expression in Algebra.  You'll learn about expressions, terms, coefficients, and more.  These definitions can confuse students but are very easy to understand by working example problems.
